INSERT INTO questoes (id, questao) values (68,'<h2 style="margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-muted); color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; margin-top: 0px !important;"><br></h2><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;">Refatore o trabalho 1, utilizando o SGBD PostgreSQL + psycopg em vez de arquivo texto puro.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;">Cada nova anotação tem: Título, Data/Hora e Descrição.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Funcionalidades:</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Cadastrar:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><li>Quando uma nova anotação é criada será possível determinar os seus atributos (0.2)</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exclusão:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><li><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Além de excluir definitivamente qualquer anotação (0.2), o Google Keep Tabajara terá também a funcionalidade de envio de anotações para Lixeira (repositório de anotações excluídas) (0.2);</p></li><li style="margin-top: 0.25em;"><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Através da Lixeira será possível restaurar anotações deletadas (0.2) e excluir definitivamente qualquer anotação (0.2);</p></li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Alterar:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><li>Alterar anotações (0.2);</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Listar:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><li><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Listar anotações (0.2);</p></li><li style="margin-top: 0.25em;"><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Ordenar por data/hora de criação (0.2);</p></li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Duplicar:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><li>Duplicar uma anotação existente (0.2);</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exigências:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><li>Utilizar psycopg e PostgreSQL (0.2)</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Prazo:</span>&nbsp;27/09</p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Valor:</span>&nbsp;2</p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Dicas:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><li>Crie uma flag (booleana) para setar as anotações que estão (e que não estão na lixeira)</li></ul>'); 

